++ Push your project to git

1. git init
2. git add .
3. git commit -m 'init project' //init project is your commit name
4. git remote add origin https://github.com/se7enntt/ReactHook.git
5. git push -u origin master

++ Clone project

- git clone https://github.com/se7enntt/ReactHook.git

++ Git check out to another brand

- git checkout -b dev
- git push -u origin master //Push to the brand is dev

- Create dicrectory and install app: (my is your app name)
  npx create-react-app my-app

- Start your app
  npm start

